---
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/gallery.css';
---
<SiteLayout title="Design System - AKALA Tools" description="AKALA Tools design system notes.">
  <main class="doc-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <h1>Design system.</h1>
        <p>Warm light UI system for small, browser-only utilities.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="card doc-card">
      <h2>Product feel</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>light, calm, and production-grade</li>
        <li>premium without looking like a heavy SaaS dashboard</li>
        <li>clear hierarchy over decoration</li>
        <li>useful in under ten seconds</li>
        <li>export/copy actions always obvious</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>Core tokens</h2>
      <pre><code>--bg: #f7f4ee;
--bg-2: #fffaf1;
--paper: #ffffff;
--ink: #17130d;
--muted: #756d62;
--line: #e4dccf;
--gold: #d99b29;</code></pre>
      <p>Full source remains in <code>docs/design-system.md</code> during the migration.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
  .doc-card {
    padding: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 34px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .doc-card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    letter-spacing: -.04em;
  }
  .doc-card h2:not(:first-child) {
    margin-top: 28px;
  }
  .doc-card pre {
    overflow: auto;
    padding: 18px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--accent-ink);
  }
</style>
